♪May stars guide us through rough waves♪

44
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:15,110
♪I give all my love unreservedly♪

45
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:25,900
Xuan.

46
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:26,700
Yes?

47
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:29,420
It feels like a dream.

48
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:36,460
Have you woken up yet?

49
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:54,500
It has been years

50
00:03:54,620 --> 00:03:57,100
since the Lingtian Palace
had a celebration.

51
00:03:57,420 --> 00:04:00,300
It must be very great today.

52
00:04:01,060 --> 00:04:01,860
Yingshi,

53
00:04:02,380 --> 00:04:05,740
I will stay and see
what is going to happen to you.

54
00:04:14,570 --> 00:04:16,950
[Memorial Table of Late Mother,
Xiao Wenqing]

55
00:04:21,700 --> 00:04:23,420
Here comes the auspicious hour.

56
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:26,460
Groom and Bride offer bows.

57
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:40,300
Good work.

58
00:04:40,660 --> 00:04:41,380
Thank you.

59
00:04:41,580 --> 00:04:42,420
Thank you.

60
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:43,380
Thank you.

61
00:04:47,980 --> 00:04:48,860
Please state your name.

62
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:50,820
I'm Zhan Yuechi of Medicine King Valley.

63
00:04:50,820 --> 00:04:52,540
I heard that Master Ling
is getting married.

64
00:04:52,780 --> 00:04:53,860
So I came here to offer congratulations.

65
00:04:53,980 --> 00:04:54,820
Zhan?

66
00:04:56,220 --> 00:04:57,580
It's Mr. Zhan from Medicine King Valley.

67
00:04:57,580 --> 00:04:58,660
Please pardon me.

68
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:01,860
But we didn't invite any sects

69
00:05:01,860 --> 00:05:04,020
in the martial arts world
to the wedding.

70
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:05,540
I wonder if you...

71
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:07,740
My sister didn't invite him.

72
00:05:07,980 --> 00:05:09,660
But I did.

73
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:15,660
What are you doing?

74
00:05:25,580 --> 00:05:26,260
Jing,

75
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,420
why are you back?

76
00:05:27,900 --> 00:05:29,500
It's the wedding
of Master Ling and Mr. Yingshi.

77
00:05:29,500 --> 00:05:30,740
Everyone in the palace is celebrating.

78
00:05:31,660 --> 00:05:32,340
So

79
00:05:32,340 --> 00:05:34,020
I brought you all some liquor.

80
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:35,540
These great brews

81
00:05:35,540 --> 00:05:37,900
are from Yipin Restaurant
down the mountain.

82
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:38,580
Brilliant.

83
00:05:38,580 --> 00:05:39,340
Buddies.

84
00:05:39,540 --> 00:05:40,220
Come and carry the liquor in.

85
00:05:40,220 --> 00:05:40,980
All right.

86
00:05:41,140 --> 00:05:41,820
Coming.

87
00:05:54,980 --> 00:05:57,700
The second bow to parents.

88
00:06:01,220 --> 00:06:03,940
Bow to each other.

89
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:09,180
Hold on.

90
00:06:18,340 --> 00:06:20,220
It was ten years ago

91
00:06:22,260 --> 00:06:24,060
that we met at Xihe Garden
in Medicine King Valley.

92
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:26,020
Do you still remember me, Xuan?

93
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:35,100
Zhan Yuechi?

94
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:38,100
It has been ten years.

95
00:06:38,540 --> 00:06:40,300
Thankfully, you recognized me.

96
00:06:42,380 --> 00:06:44,700
Mr. Zhan, you came uninvited
and disrupted the ceremony.

97
00:06:44,860 --> 00:06:46,300
I wonder why.

98
00:06:47,460 --> 00:06:49,540
I was told
that you were about to get married.

99
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:51,820
I was afraid you would be deceived

100
00:06:52,140 --> 00:06:53,340
and marry the wrong man.

101
00:06:53,740 --> 00:06:55,660
Hence, I hurried here day and night.

102
00:06:57,940 --> 00:06:59,140
It has been a really long while.

103
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:00,740
Tang Yan.

104
00:07:06,180 --> 00:07:07,180
Who did you just call?

105
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:09,980
Why don't you tell her

106
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:11,780
who Tang Yan is?

107
00:07:16,180 --> 00:07:17,060
No?

108
00:07:17,380 --> 00:07:18,140
Fine.

109
00:07:18,540 --> 00:07:20,260
I will say it for you.

110
00:07:21,980 --> 00:07:22,900
From what I know,

111
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:25,020
the current leader of the Shadow Sect
in Lingtian Palace

112
00:07:25,020 --> 00:07:26,220
is called Bai Chen.

113
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:28,580
You saved him ten years ago.

114
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:30,700
So he stays to repay your favor.

115
00:07:31,580 --> 00:07:32,740
That's true.

116
00:07:33,060 --> 00:07:34,220
But the fact is,

117
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:37,340
the person before us isn't Bai Chen.

118
00:07:41,220 --> 00:07:42,140
His name is Tang Yan.

119
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:44,260
He was once my father's adopted son.

120
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:46,620
He betrayed Medicine King Valley
and fled ten years ago.

121
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:48,020
He has disappeared since then.

122
00:07:48,380 --> 00:07:49,860
We thought he was dead.

123
00:07:50,820 --> 00:07:52,060
Unexpectedly,

124
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:55,060
he snuck into the Shadow Sect

125
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:57,900
and became the leader.

126
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:01,540
Is what he said

127
00:08:02,820 --> 00:08:04,260
true?

128
00:08:21,540 --> 00:08:23,060
Starting from today,

129
00:08:24,140 --> 00:08:25,620
you are me.

130
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:29,020
This is the proof between her and me.

131
00:08:30,100 --> 00:08:31,900
Don't forget your promise.

132
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:33,820
Return her favor for me.

133
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:34,820
Don't worry.

134
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,220
I won't forget.

135
00:08:36,380 --> 00:08:37,580
I

136
00:08:37,580 --> 00:08:38,660
will avenge you

137
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:41,260
and repay her kindness.

138
00:08:42,020 --> 00:08:43,340
From today on,

139
00:08:44,020 --> 00:08:45,340
I'm Bai Chen.

140
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:49,340
If there is a chance,

141
00:08:50,060 --> 00:08:52,140
please visit my sister.

142
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:53,860
You must

143
00:08:56,010 --> 00:08:57,500
survive.

144
00:09:17,180 --> 00:09:18,900
Tang Yan betrayed Medicine King Valley

145
00:09:19,140 --> 00:09:20,340
and then infiltrated Lingtian Palace,

146
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:22,500
and he stole someone's identity

147
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:23,740
to win your trust.

148
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:25,820
He is scheming,

149
00:09:25,820 --> 00:09:26,740
and he orchestrated all these.

150
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:27,900
Xuan,

151
00:09:28,180 --> 00:09:30,060
this man is despicable.

152
00:09:31,540 --> 00:09:32,340
Xuan.

153
00:09:32,900 --> 00:09:35,020
I received the news suddenly.

154
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:36,580
I don't want you to be fooled.

155
00:09:36,940 --> 00:09:37,940
Hence...

156
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:42,020
Thank you

157
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:44,420
for informing me of this, Mr. Zhan.

158
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:47,620
However, this is the affair
of Lingtian Palace.

159
00:09:48,580 --> 00:09:50,380
Mr. Zhan,

160
00:09:50,620 --> 00:09:51,900
please leave.

161
00:09:52,380 --> 00:09:53,180
Xuan...

162
00:10:12,620 --> 00:10:15,940
♪If hand waves are
the prelude to farewell♪

163
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:19,540
♪If words hold no intention to stall♪

164
00:10:20,100 --> 00:10:21,820
♪Goodbye♪

165
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:25,860
♪Should be reserved
for when our lives are at stake♪

166
00:10:27,140 --> 00:10:30,470
♪If time rushes swiftly
like wind and dust♪

167
00:10:30,860 --> 00:10:34,180
♪If tears come before words
after waking up♪

168
00:10:34,580 --> 00:10:36,860
♪May you not be drowned in bitterness♪

169
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:38,460
♪I only wish your eyes♪

170
00:10:38,620 --> 00:10:41,540
♪As pure as snow♪
